      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This purist-spec example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, producing 333 hp with a linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, while the variable M-differential ensures precise torque distribution. Mechanically, this chassis is exceptional: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been preemptively reinforced for structural integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping profile with no bushing deflection. The exterior retains its original deep luster, and the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear. A meticulously maintained specimen with a complete service dossier.",
